B.WQ=new A.ao("The portfolio of our marketing team is not only to invite salvage buyers already registered with us but also find new potential buyers from the internet and adding them up as well as educating them to participate in the e-Auctions. Transparency is the most important word in salvaging. To realise the highest possible value of damaged, dead, obsolete and unwanted assets, the key is a competitive approach with the participation of maximum participants in a forward e-Auction. Our marketing team continuously thrives for the same and are always on the lookout for end users thus increasing the value of the salvage.",null,B.d5,null,null,null,null,null,null)
